        void onConnectedState(Beacon beacon,
                      int newState,
                      int status)
        callback of beacon connection state
        Parameters:
        beacon - current beacon
        newState - Return the new connection state of iBeacon. Can be one of CONNECTED or DISCONNECTED. See Beacon.CONNECTED and Beacon.DISCONNECTED
        status - Return the result of callback.Can be one of SUCCESS or FAILURE. See SensoroBeaconConnection.SUCCESS and SensoroBeaconConnection.FAILURE
